race.comment: SPECIAL PROPHET (8) has been thereabouts without striking, beaten less than a length in his last two. Gets in light with the claim and can give a bold sight over the longer journey. MIDNIGHT AFFAIR (6) looks primed for the rise in trip after some sound chasing efforts. Her form earlier in the prep lines up well and if she can recapture that form she is right up to this. Backs up quickly and looms a big threat. WILL TO EXCEL (1) is knocking on the door and should be hitting his straps now. In the mix. FINAL IMPACT (5) was a flashing light last start when stepping back out in trip. Gets in well with the claim and is in the mix.
